OL,3,CBy-election results confirmed in Sark
OL,5,FThe results of the by-election for
OL,6,FChief Pleas in Sark have been
OL,7,Fannounced this evening, with two
OL,8,Fcandidates confirmed as the island's
OL,9,Fnext Conseillers.
OL,11,FJoseph Perree and Michael Lanyon
OL,12,Freceived the most votes to serve on
OL,13,FChief Pleas, with 152 and 97 votes,
OL,14,Frespectively.
OL,16,FThey will both serve until December,
OL,17,Fwhen the island is due for a general
OL,18,Felection.
