OL,3,CBy-election results confirmed in Sark
OL,5,FFour candidates were running for two
OL,6,FConseiller seats on Chief Pleas, after
OL,7,Fone politician resigned in October due
OL,8,Fto leadership concerns, while another
OL,9,Fpolitician left in January for
OL,10,Fpersonal reasons.
OL,12,FThe unsuccessful candidates were
OL,13,FSebastien Moerman, who received 96
OL,14,Fvotes, and Antony Dunks, who received
OL,15,F49 votes.
OL,17,FThere was a voter turnout of 56%.
